OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA generally fair days weather
OL,6,Fin prospect, mostly dry with periods
OL,7,Fof sunshine through this morning,
OL,8,Fbefore turning hazy from the west
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon. Winds light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry this evening with some
OL,12,Flate bright periods. Meanwhile light
OL,13,Fand patchy rain spreads in to affect
OL,14,Fwestern areas, but most places in the
OL,15,Feast remaining dry.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FCloudy with a few spots of
OL,18,Flight rain, but mainly dry with some
OL,19,Fbrighter spells for Moray. Outbreaks
OL,20,Fof rain will then spread northeast
OL,21,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
